# agentic-sdk adapter machinery (regenerated by bootstrap-project).
#
# Invariant: an installed repo commits no AI-agent machinery, only durable
# project-specific state. Track exactly:
#   .agentic-sdk/project.edn   the descriptor (lanes, permissions, modules)
#   .agentic-sdk/artifacts/    durable project docs (planning, ADRs, notes)
# Everything else the SDK touches is regenerated by bootstrap-project on each
# machine: the .claude/ and .opencode/ adapters, the root CLAUDE.md (a
# standard symlink into .agentic-sdk/templates/), and the masters, spine, and
# state under .agentic-sdk/.

# The whole .claude/ adapter (settings.json, hook symlinks) is regenerated
# from the descriptor's :hooks and :permissions.
.claude/

# The whole .opencode/ adapter (agent projection, plugin, config) is
# regenerated by opencode-sync and bootstrap-project.
.opencode/

# The root router is a standard symlink to .agentic-sdk/templates/CLAUDE.md;
# identical across projects, never hand-edited.
/CLAUDE.md

# Under .agentic-sdk/: ignore the snapped/symlinked masters, the spine, and
# all runtime state; track only the descriptor and the artifacts tree.
.agentic-sdk/*
!.agentic-sdk/project.edn
!.agentic-sdk/artifacts/
!.agentic-sdk/artifacts/**

